{"tid":1621791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"與怪獸戰鬥的人小心自已不要也變成了怪獸","createTime":"2019-10-04T14:49:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:56:29.000Z","uid":49202,"like":183,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"ccf004a56e505408543305f00775737580094762","tid":1621791,"uid":49202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:49:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CfD6co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CfD6co.jpg&h=56195385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n提醒下各位前線手足<br />\n行動前都一定要思考下做呢個行為背後既原因同必要性<br />\n例如係幫黨鐵裝修係因為佢與民為敵<br />\n出賣香港人等<br />\n私了打人斬人藍絲係因為法律制裁唔到佢<br />\n所以要教訓下佢<br />\n做任何違反現有法律既事必須要有一個合理原則又可以被理解<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇原則 行為又唔被認同既時候就同真暴徒 知法犯法既黑警冇分別架啦<br />\n希望你地明我既意思啦<br />\n辛苦哂"},{"pid":"ed2208db5a3b5664bb2c67ef4843dc86125e3593","tid":1621791,"uid":49202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:53:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e920dbb879202a5e67fe4649ec44d373eb171ad0","tid":1621791,"uid":162711,"like":30,"dislike":5,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:53:48.000Z","msg":"勇武唔同暴力啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 千其唔好走火入魔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歷史話俾我哋知即使最後成功都只係會由一個極權變成另一個極權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9206cd982a102b986a19ea3a6f4b9a8e8b3b9189","tid":1621791,"uid":94771,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:53:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果係檢討可以接受"},{"pid":"15ab2696c15df6e31e27e48400e11c898c0090c6","tid":1621791,"uid":251551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T14:53:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl