:0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:01:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"24901ecc04c869f04574b0456c63d6c57ddcfbef","tid":1621791,"uid":62402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:01:50.000Z","msg":"輕推呢個post"},{"pid":"6114b855505f171764db8f8a4872d7606be4473c","tid":1621791,"uid":49202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c27bd24966d25b39372844ef28601109522629c","tid":1621791,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zsrvPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zsrvPS.jpg&h=5d567c19&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"岩呀 就係要呢d<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n齊做文宣"},{"pid":"1313b3989af77495cf9f2d3a084dbce145fe684f","tid":1621791,"uid":251551,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"又係呢D限制升級 制肘自己友既論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用尼采既說話黎曲線左膠維穩<br />\n<br />\nBuy既人麻煩回憶下過去三個月 <br />\n遠既記唔起 近既都記得掛？"},{"pid":"2fba534b353d3f65499d8ad124e2ef01229a3107","tid":1621791,"uid":51625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:02:57.000Z","msg":"經過1／10一役，班狗認為自己已經可以亂咁開槍射擊市民，所以我哋係時候要另闢戰線。<br />\n<br />\n我認為光復香港，時代革命唔單止要打爆林鄭同黑警之外，我哋更加要令呢個香港不再一樣。<br />\n<br />\n首先，大家要知道香港社會不嬲都無將人當喺人咁嚟看待，一個人嘅價值係建基於佢擁有幾多嘢、做到幾多嘢、外表打扮得如何，而唔係佢本身就有價值。<br />\n<br />\n喺呢一點，已經同西方文明社會有差別，如果大家覺得要學習西方文明社會嘅同時，覺得呢樣嘢係唔需要改嘅話，我諗大家真係可以番屋企訓。<br />\n<br />\n正正係呢一點，令到香港社會出現咗好多社會問題，包括超長工時、低工資等問題，同時亦都係黑警埋沒良知、對市民濫暴嘅真正原因。<br />\n<br />\n所以如果要光復香港嘅話，呢個觀念一定要改變，否則香港真係只會好似以前一樣，依舊一樣。"},{"pid":"6bd2b191fbe508aabc80a5c0fb78b8d81499d993","tid":1621791,"uid":30988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:04:07.000Z","msg":"我不欲受傷，更不欲兄弟受傷。<br />\n如果令惡人受傷可以捍衛兄弟，我義不容辭。<br />\n<br />\n為了這世界的和平與自由，人有時是要拿起槍技的，<br />\n正如二戰時邱吉爾所選擇的道路。邱吉是怪獸嗎？不是<br />\n<br />\n我呢篇文可以詳細答你<br />\n[給梁天琦]我們並沒有被仇恨衝昏頭腦<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/aiyaOvV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/aiyaOvV</a>"},{"pid":"dc2a8c45d4a1c40fe4c8858d275e21af9ec08778","tid":1621791,"uid":168522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:04:57.000Z","msg":"保持理性<br />\n對準政權"},{"pid":"3f1b34c6e0861b996f5e18752ea9d0aa09cfc21e","tid":1621791,"uid":258770,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"add0b664de8f64a29cd896b14d3752e3392b8986","tid":1621791,"uid":73915,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:00:47.000Z","msg":"唔係怪獸，點對付怪獸？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:05:30.000Z","msg":"以武制暴唔代表濫暴<br />\n打怪獸就變超人 唔好變怪獸"},{"pid":"95c03ddaedff277f86ffb1eb435c9cbdf6371f3f","tid":1621791,"uid":202173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:05:39.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"74931a6b1ebb0804b485972e9b1362e0bd8d5e55","tid":1621791,"uid":33577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:06:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72a202d9257874b10f1f2f5abdc9a0938cd7b254","tid":1621791,"uid":71133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:07:30.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"c2abe6feb4c51fcd426862d0df21615821a71693","tid":1621791,"uid":42740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:07:40.000Z","msg":"荃灣咪完美<br />\n一邊裝修一邊對傳媒講罪狀"},{"pid":"10eda9cea723471fc68012933c6e7cf44e2278dd","tid":1621791,"uid":49202,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1313b3989af77495cf9f2d3a084dbce145fe684f","tid":1621791,"uid":251551,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:02:44.000Z","msg":"又係呢D限制升級 制肘自己友既論調<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用尼采既說話黎曲線左膠維穩<br />\n<br />\nBuy既人麻煩回憶下過去三個月 <br />\n遠既記唔起 近既都記得掛？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"升級絕對冇問題 但一定要有原則<br />\n燒黨鐵我覺得ok<br />\n上面有幅圖我覺得幾好"},{"pid":"7aed610203681d0c175e50e7648a80f9cf6a5271","tid":1621791,"uid":234698,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:10:53.000Z","msg":"對準政權，對付建制派"},{"pid":"6a3f645219c79db365b97fc81b7a48f0ea495d50","tid":1621791,"uid":70524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:11:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">612 中信大廈<br />\n721 元朗恐襲<br />\n831 太子死人<br />\n917 黨鐵出軌<br />\n101 國殤紀念<br />\n104 緊急惡法<br />\n新屋嶺謀殺強姦營<br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c73690171e86f3d42d0d2d5804210284c2de4a93","tid":1621791,"uid":151352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:12:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"a9cbe712fa9d5f3078fc465095de40b34691cfcb","tid":1621791,"uid":202173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c27bd24966d25b39372844ef28601109522629c","tid":1621791,"uid":154486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:00:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zsrvPS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zsrvPS.jpg&h=5d567c19&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:12:50.000Z","msg":"推，大家落到場周圍一定有好多挑戰挑釁<br />\n周圍有人唔同意係預咗既事，千萬唔好意氣用事<br />\n<br />\n只係出聲話我地搞事個啲，唔使埋佢，更加唔好哂時間去理論<br />\n如果只係阻住既就搵人拉開佢，真係郁手郁腳既就自己睇路鶳咗佢<br />\n<br />\n而家出咗緊急法對家一定會千方百計去抹黑我哋係是非不分既暴徒<br />\n特別而家不斷有風向話要連員工，普通市民都打<br />\n大家要沉住氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"426f6eb5d642e0da5b925080f7873e9a0c7c25d1","tid":1621791,"uid":74091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T15:12:52.000Z","msg":"p"},{"pid"